articles.author: Aaditya Narayan
articles.title: Neeraj Chopra set to start high-stakes 2024 Olympic season at Doha Diamond League - ESPN India
articles.description: Neeraj Chopra will be joined by his compatriot Kishore Kumar Jena at the Doha Diamond League, in both of their first competitions since last year's epic battle at the Asian Games.
articles.content: It's that time of the year again. Neeraj Chopra is back in action and this year the stakes are even higher. India's greatest ever athlete is set to begin his 2024 season at the Doha Diamond League on… [+3741 chars]
